{"tid":2162403,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"智秀終於做女主角！","createTime":"2020-08-18T06:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T02:44:59.000Z","uid":320858,"like":42,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"193ca593c12b7726502b9a07bda3047ba72a5315","tid":2162403,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:12:37.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK智秀選上《雪滴花》女主人公 第一次主演挑戰，將開始演技活動。<br />\n<br />\n 18日所屬社YG方面表示：&ldquo;智秀確定出演JTBC新電視劇《雪滴花》（暫譯）。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n 《雪滴花》是JTBC《天空之城》的導演趙賢卓和作家劉賢美意氣相投的作品，現在正在討論JTBC的編排。<br />\n 智秀將通過《雪滴花》首次挑戰電視劇主演。 之前出演過KBS2電視劇《製作人》和tvN電視劇《阿斯達年代記》的智秀能否通過《雪滴花》正式邁出演技偶像的步伐備受關注。"},{"pid":"6d78171f391abe6af2c0f160b4c00b5b1a7fb5ae","tid":2162403,"uid":320858,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12NwXFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12NwXFM.jpg&h=bfda01ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0Z7v0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0Z7v0N.jpg&h=ff257dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDwE6y7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDwE6y7.jpg&h=61dcaee2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0H8ZT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0H8ZT8.jpg&h=b4d07ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVFFQ0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVFFQ0P.jpg&h=b9ee7777&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHjLhFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHjLhFQ.jpg&h=cf42343c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rndTrza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrndTrza.jpg&h=c2e950c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UJd4yeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUJd4yeb.jpg&